Description: This registry defines the Redfish Device Enablement messages for Redfish

RDETaskCompleted.Description: Indicates that the RDE device finished running the Task of RDE Operations successfully.
RDETaskCompleted.Message: RDE device has completed the long-running Task for RDE Operations and without errors.

RDETaskFailed.Description: Indicates that the RDE device failed to complete the Task of RDE Operations because of errors.
RDETaskFailed.Message: RDE device fails to complete the long-running Task for RDE Operations. %1

RDETaskRunning.Description: Indicates that the long-running Task for RDE Operation is still running.
RDETaskRunning.Message: The long-running Task is still running by RDE device for the RDE Operations.

RDETaskSpawned.Description: Indicates that the RDE device spawns a long-running Task when executed RDE Operations.
RDETaskSpawned.Message: A long-running Task has spawned when RDE device executed RDE Operations.

Name: RedfishDeviceEnablement Message Registry
